article.linkText: CSU Northridge secures 84-48 victory over Mississippi Valley State
article.story: NORTHRIDGE, Calif. -- — Keonte Jones' 17 points helped CSU Northridge defeat Mississippi Valley State 84-48 on Friday. Jones added nine rebounds for the Matadors (4-2). De'Sean Allen-Eikens scored 14 points and Jasman Sangha added 13. The Delta Devils (0-6) were led by Rayquan Brown, who recorded 20 points. ------ The Associated Press created this story using technology provided by Data Skrive and data from Sportradar.
